ap-type: initial !important; scroll-target-group: initial !important; scroll-timeline: initial !important; scrollbar-color: initial !important; scrollbar-gutter: initial !important; scrollbar-width: initial !important; shape-image-threshold: initial !important; shape-margin: initial !important; shape-outside: initial !important; shape-rendering: initial !important; size: initial !important; speak: initial !important; stop-color: initial !important; stop-opacity: initial !important; stroke: initial !important; stroke-dasharray: initial !important; stroke-dashoffset: initial !important; stroke-linecap: initial !important; stroke-linejoin: initial !important; stroke-miterlimit: initial !important; stroke-opacity: initial !important; stroke-width: initial !important; tab-size: initial !important; table-layout: initial !important; text-align: inherit !important; text-align-last: initial !important; text-anchor: initial !important; text-autospace: initial !important; text-box: initial !important; text-combine-upright: initial !important; text-decoration-line: underline !important; text-decoration-style: dotted !important; text-decoration-skip-ink: initial !important; text-emphasis: initial !important; text-emphasis-position: initial !important; text-indent: initial !important; text-overflow: initial !important; text-shadow: initial !important; text-transform: initial !important; text-underline-offset: initial !important; text-underline-position: initial !important; text-wrap: initial !important; timeline-scope: initial !important; touch-action: initial !important; transform: initial !important; transform-box: initial !important; transform-origin: initial !important; transform-style: initial !important; transition: initial !important; translate: initial !important; user-select: initial !important; vector-effect: initial !important; vertical-align: initial !important; view-timeline: initial !important; view-transition-class: initial !important; view-transition-group: initial !important; view-transition-name: initial !important; visibility: inherit !important; border-spacing: initial !important; -webkit-box-align: initial !important; -webkit-box-decoration-break: initial !important; -webkit-box-direction: initial !important; -webkit-box-flex: initial !important; -webkit-box-ordinal-group: initial !important; -webkit-box-orient: initial !important; -webkit-box-pack: initial !important; -webkit-box-reflect: initial !important; -webkit-line-break: initial !important; -webkit-line-clamp: initial !important; -webkit-mask-box-image: initial !important; -webkit-rtl-ordering: initial !important; -webkit-ruby-position: initial !important; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: initial !important; -webkit-text-combine: initial !important; -webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: initial !important; -webkit-text-fill-color: unset !important; -webkit-text-security: initial !important; -webkit-text-stroke: initial !important; -webkit-user-drag: initial !important; white-space-collapse: initial !important; widows: initial !important; width: initial !important; will-change: initial !important; word-break: initial !important; word-spacing: initial !important; x: initial !important; y: initial !important; z-index: initial !important;\">EMTEL</span></a></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;cobra una relevancia crucial. Su compromiso de llevar tecnología de última generación a cada rincón del municipio, tanto en la zona urbana como en la rural, es un pilar para el desarrollo y la inclusión</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">La llegada de una conexión a internet rápida y confiable a las zonas rurales no solo acorta la brecha digital, sino que también abre un abanico de oportunidades. Permite a los agricultores acceder a información actualizada sobre mercados y técnicas de cultivo, a los estudiantes continuar su educación a distancia y a los pequeños emprendedores expandir su negocio más allá de las fronteras locales. . La conectividad no es solo un servicio, es una herramienta de empoderamiento</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.563em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Confianza y cercanía&nbsp;</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El lema «si nos ven acércate» refleja una filosofía de cercanía y atención personalizada que genera confianza en la comunidad. En un mercado a menudo impersonal, el contacto directo y la disposición a ofrecer «las mejores ofertas» no es solo una estrategia de marketing, sino un compromiso con las necesidades reales de los ciudadanos. Esta proximidad es lo que transforma a un proveedor de servicios en un verdadero socio para el progreso</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759188039_WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-11-at-09.06.01-1065x570.jpeg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:20:39', '2025-09-29 23:20:39', '', '', ''),
(18, 'Un Camino de Compromiso y Arraigo en el Cauca', 'un-camino-de-compromiso-y-arraigo-en-el-cauca', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En un panorama político a menudo marcado por la desconfianza, la figura de *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Walter Aldana*</span>&nbsp;emerge en el departamento del Cauca con una propuesta que resuena con valores de honestidad y amor por la tierra. *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Su campaña, con miras al Congreso en 2026,*</span>&nbsp;se distancia de los fastos tradicionales para abrazar la&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">austeridad y el estoicismo</span>. No son grandes caravanas o discursos pomposos los que definen su camino, sino una forma de pisar las tierras caucana, donde su palabra busca ser un genuino reflejo de compromiso.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">*En estos tiempos donde la credibilidad de la clase política está en entredicho, el enfoque de Aldana parece estar ganando terreno</span>.* El apoyo para su aspiración como Representante a la Cámara crece, no por promesas vacías, sino por el trabajo constante que ha dedicado a las comunidades más necesitadas y excluidas del departamento. Su labor, enfocada en llevar *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">apoyo y bienestar a los más pobres*</span>, es el pilar sobre el que se construye su campaña.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Esta combinación de compromiso y profundo arraigo con su gente no pasa desapercibida.*</span>&nbsp;Un líder del macizo colombiano, al ser consultado sobre *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Aldana, lo define como una esperanza para aquellos que creen que el pueblo sí puede tener representantes que trabajen por su bienestar.*</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Esta labor la ha emprendido de la mano de su amigo, el senador *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Ferney Silva</span>,* formando una dupla que se perfila como una fuerza importante para quienes anhelan una representación política más cercana y humana.</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759188166_ALDANA-1.jpeg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:22:46', '2025-09-29 23:22:46', '', '', ''),
(19, 'Un llamado al deber: La nueva generación de guardianes en el Cauca', 'un-llamado-al-deber-la-nueva-generacion-de-guardianes-en-el-cauca', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">En esta sección inicial, puedes capturar la atención del lector presentando el hecho noticioso:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">50 jóvenes del Cauca</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;se están formando como auxiliares de policía. Resalta el valor de esta iniciativa, describiéndola como un paso crucial para fortalecer la seguridad en la región. Utiliza un tono esperanzador, destacando la importancia de que estos jóvenes, «hombres de la tierra», se conviertan en los futuros protectores de sus propias comunidades. Puedes mencionar que esta formación no es solo una oportunidad profesional, sino también un&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">acto de servicio y vocación</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.563em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Disciplina y Vocación: Los pilares de un héroe</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Aquí, desglosa los conceptos de&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">disciplina y vocación</span>&nbsp;mencionados en el texto. Explora por qué estos dos valores son esenciales para la carrera policial.</p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.14286em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: square; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Disciplina:</span>&nbsp;Argumenta que la disciplina es la base de la efectividad y la confianza en la policía. Es lo que les permite mantener el orden, seguir protocolos y actuar con profesionalismo incluso en las situaciones más difíciles.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Vocación:</span>&nbsp;Reflexiona sobre la vocación de servicio. La vocación es lo que impulsa a estos jóvenes a arriesgar su vida por los demás, a trabajar por el bienestar de su comunidad y a ver su labor no solo como un trabajo, sino como una misión. Este es el espíritu de «Dios y Patria», un compromiso con valores superiores que guían su labor diaria</li></ul>', 'public/images/blog/1759189044_ponal.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:37:24', '2025-09-29 23:37:24', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `blog_posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `image`, `author`, `status`, `deleted`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`) VALUES
(20, 'La Vega, Centro de la Transformación: Cuando la Comunidad Ejecuta la Promesa de Gobierno', 'la-vega-centro-de-la-transformacion-cuando-la-comunidad-ejecuta-la-promesa-de-gobierno', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">La reciente visita a&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La Vega</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">, liderada por el Gobernador Octavio Guzmán y acompañada por la Secretaria de Gobierno, Maribel Perafan, trasciende el significado de un simple acto político. Se ha convertido en una&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">demostración palpable</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;de que&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">#LaFuerzadelPueblo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;no es solo un eslogan, sino un motor de gestión que&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">cumple</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;en los sectores más vitales:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">salud, educación, agricultura, infraestructura y ambiente</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">.</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0.83em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.953em; line-height: 1.35; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Dignificar la Vida: Un Enfoque Integral</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El anuncio de cumplimiento en un abanico tan amplio de áreas subraya una visión de&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">desarrollo integral</span>. No se trata de inversiones aisladas, sino de una estrategia orquestada que busca&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">dignificar la vida de los caucanos y las caucanas</span>&nbsp;desde múltiples frentes:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.14286em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: square; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Salud y Educación:</span>&nbsp;Asegurando el capital humano, la base para que las comunidades puedan prosperar.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Agricultura:</span>&nbsp;Fortaleciendo la vocación productiva del Macizo caucano, garantizando ingresos y seguridad alimentaria.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Infraestructura (Vías Para La Vida):</span>&nbsp;Conectando el territorio, abriendo mercados y permitiendo el acceso a servicios esenciales, lo que es crucial para la paz y la economía rural.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Ambiente:</span>&nbsp;Reconociendo la importancia del Macizo en la regulación hídrica y climática, y actuando con responsabilidad frente a los recursos naturales.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Esta aproximación holística es la que realmente cimienta el desarrollo sostenible en el Cauca.</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759189278_maribel-1-1140x570.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:41:18', '2025-09-29 23:41:18', '', '', ''),
(21, 'Tragedia y Muerte en Cada Trago: La Amenaza Silenciosa del Licor Adulterado', 'tragedia-y-muerte-en-cada-trago-la-amenaza-silenciosa-del-licor-adulterado', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Barranquilla vive horas de luto y angustia tras la muerte de&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">seis personas</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;y la hospitalización de cuatro más en la UCI, víctimas de la intoxicación por consumir&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">licor adulterado</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">, popularmente conocido como ‘Picho’. Esta tragedia, que se repite con dolorosa frecuencia en el país, expone una falla crítica en la salud pública, la seguridad y la vigilancia de las autoridades. No estamos hablando de un accidente; estamos hablando de&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">crímenes</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;motivados por la codicia</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0.83em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.953em; line-height: 1.35; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">La Causa: Avaricia Ciega y Metanol Letal</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El licor «elaborado artesanalmente» que cobró la vida de&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Nicolás Manuel Medrano, Helmot Enrique Escolar, José Felipe Crespo Ortiz, Emiro Alberto Miranda</span>&nbsp;y dos personas más sin identificar, es una sentencia de muerte disfrazada de fiesta barata. Detrás de estas muertes no está el alcohol etílico que buscaban las víctimas, sino el&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">metanol</span>, una sustancia tóxica y mortal que se utiliza para abaratar costos, pero que destruye el sistema nervioso central, causa ceguera y, finalmente, la muerte.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La venta y distribución de este veneno es un acto de&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">terrorismo económico</span>&nbsp;contra los más vulnerables. Quienes consumen estos licores de bajo costo son, a menudo, personas con escasos recursos que buscan un momento de esparcimiento. Los fabricantes y vendedores de ‘Picho’ saben perfectamente el riesgo que están comercializando. Su delito no es solo contrabando o evasión fiscal; es un delito contra la salud pública y la vida.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 0.83em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.953em; line-height: 1.35; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">La Urgencia de la Respuesta Estatal</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La tragedia, ocurrida el pasado martes, 23 de septiembre, exige una respuesta mucho más robusta que los llamados a la precaución. Las autoridades deben atacar este flagelo en dos frentes:</p><ol start=\"1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.14286em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Justicia y Persecución Criminal:</span>&nbsp;Es fundamental que la Fiscalía identifique y capture a los responsables de la fabricación, distribución y venta de estos licores adulterados. Estas personas deben ser juzgadas por homicidio. La pena debe ser ejemplar para desincentivar este comercio ilegal que prioriza las ganancias por encima de la vida humana. Las etiquetas de «contrabando» o «violación de la propiedad industrial» se quedan cortas; esto es&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">asesinato en masa por lucro</span>.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Vigilancia y Prevención Activa:</span>&nbsp;La Policía y las secretarías de Salud deben intensificar las&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">redadas y operativos</span>&nbsp;permanentes en los puntos de venta y, crucialmente, en los centros de producción. La ineficacia en el control permite que el ‘Picho’ se normalice en los barrios y centros de la ciudad. Se necesita una estrategia de&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">inteligencia policial</span>&nbsp;que desmantele estas redes, no solo incautar unas cuantas botellas</li></ol>', 'public/images/blog/1759189398_quilla-1140x570.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:43:18', '2025-09-29 23:43:18', '', '', ''),
(22, 'La Brecha entre el Papel y la Calle una Realidad que el Gobierno Nacional Quiere Ocultar del Cauca', 'la-brecha-entre-el-papel-y-la-calle-una-realidad-que-el-gobierno-nacional-quiere-ocultar-del-cauca', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El gobierno habla de estadísticas de seguridad, pero en el Cauca la realidad es otra. Mientras en Bogotá se discuten cifras de homicidios que supuestamente van a la baja, aquí, en nuestras veredas y municipios, la vida se ha vuelto una ruleta rusa. *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Los secuestros de Guido, de Óscar Jordán «el Mocho» de Padilla, y el hijo de Samuel no son solo titulares, son el reflejo de una herida profunda que el Estado no logra sanar.*</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La seguridad no se puede medir únicamente con números<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">. *Una estadística que muestra una ligera disminución de la criminalidad no significa nada cuando el miedo es la constante en la cotidianidad*.</span>&nbsp;La gente del Cauca no siente que está más segura; todo lo contrario. Se siente más vulnerable que nunca. Este contraste entre el discurso oficial y la realidad es una burla para quienes viven bajo el yugo de los grupos armados y delincuenciales.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Estos grupos han logrado *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">consolidar su control territorial*</span>&nbsp;de una forma alarmante, aprovechando la débil presencia del Estado. El secuestro se ha convertido en una forma de financiación y en una herramienta de intimidación. No se trata solo de dinero, sino de demostrar quién tiene el poder en la región</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Detrás de cada secuestro hay una familia que se desgarra, una comunidad que se silencia y un futuro que se desvanece<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">. *La frialdad de las estadísticas no puede capturar el dolor de una madre que espera noticias de su hijo, ni la angustia de un empresario que ya no puede trabajar con tranquilidad</span></p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"filled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 280px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_4_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 280px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: visible;\"></div></ins></div>', 'public/images/blog/1759189574_654-1-682x570.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:46:14', '2025-09-29 23:46:14', '', '', ''),
(23, 'La delgada línea entre un chisme y un delito en la era digital', 'la-delgada-linea-entre-un-chisme-y-un-delito-en-la-era-digital', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En la vorágine de las redes sociales y los grupos de mensajería, el chisme se ha vuelto una moneda de cambio rápida y, a menudo, destructiva. Lo que antes era una conversación susurrada en una esquina, hoy se amplifica y viraliza en cuestión de segundos, alcanzando a miles de personas. Sin embargo, lo que muchos consideran un simple cotilleo, puede cruzar una línea muy peligrosa y convertirse en un delito con graves consecuencias.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El video destaca el artículo 442 del Código Penal, una disposición legal que protege a las personas de la difamación, especialmente cuando se realiza a través de plataformas digitales. No se trata solo de un regaño moral; estamos hablando de una acción legal que puede resultar en penas de prisión y multas significativas. Este es un recordatorio crucial de que la libertad de expresión no es absoluta y conlleva una enorme responsabilidad.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_4_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_4\" name=\"aswift_4\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=4248172323&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.12~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759189624&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fgeneral%2Fla-delgada-linea-entre-un-chisme-y-un-delito-en-la-era-digital%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759189623885&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=1229&amp;idt=2&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759189418%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759189418%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759189418%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280%2C726x280&amp;nras=2&amp;correlator=6629850591228&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=6&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=1510&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31094694%2C31094857%2C31094918%2C95372358%2C42533293%2C95344790%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=5180586878603637&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fgeneral%2Fla-brecha-entre-el-papel-y-la-calle-una-realidad-que-el-gobierno-nacional-quiere-ocultar-del-cauca%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=272\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-query-id=\"COmKnPOT_48DFdhZ9ggd49A20A\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La velocidad con la que un rumor se propaga en un grupo de WhatsApp o en una red social como Instagram o TikTok es alarmante. Una reputación que tardó años en construirse puede ser destruida en minutos por un comentario malintencionado o una mentira. La ley reconoce este daño, y por eso, la pena por difamación se agrava cuando el chisme se «viraliza». No es una simple sanción, es un mensaje claro: la impunidad digital no existe</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Este tema nos obliga a reflexionar sobre nuestra propia conducta en línea. Antes de compartir ese meme, ese rumor, o ese comentario, debemos detenernos y preguntarnos: ¿qué impacto tendrá en la vida de otra persona? ¿Estoy contribuyendo a la destrucción de su reputación? ¿Podría esta acción tener consecuencias legales para mí?</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La era digital ha democratizado la comunicación, pero también ha puesto en nuestras manos un poder inmenso: el poder de dañar. Es hora de que seamos más conscientes de nuestras acciones, de que entendamos que detrás de cada perfil hay una persona real, y de que la justicia, aunque a veces lenta, tiene la capacidad de alcanzarnos incluso en el mundo virtual. Defender la propia reputación es un derecho, y la ley venezolana ofrece herramientas para hacerlo. Es fundamental que todos estemos informados para proteger no solo nuestra imagen, sino también la de los demás.</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759189697_eee-1140x570.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:48:17', '2025-09-29 23:48:17', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `blog_posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `image`, `author`, `status`, `deleted`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`) VALUES
(24, 'La Inversión Social, la Gran Ausente del Presupuesto!', 'la-inversion-social-la-gran-ausente-del-presupuesto', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El reciente debate en la *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Comisión Tercera del Senado, capturado en el video, revela una profunda frustración con la gestión del gobierno actual. La intervención del Senador Ciro Ramírez no es solo un reclamo*</span>, es un grito de alarma sobre las prioridades económicas que parecen haber abandonado la inversión social, a pesar de la promesa de *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">«gobierno del cambio»*.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">*La crítica de Ramírez*</span>&nbsp;es incisiva y dolorosamente precisa. El Senador cuestiona un *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">presupuesto*</span>&nbsp;que, en lugar de priorizar a la gente, parece estar destinado a otros fines. *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Nos hace reflexionar: ¿para qué sirve un presupuesto si no se invierte en lo que realmente importa?*</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En la intervención, se enumeran recortes significativos que golpean directamente a los ciudadanos más vulnerables:</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.14286em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: square; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">*Vivienda</span>:* Se recortan 1.7 billones de pesos, un golpe directo a la posibilidad de que miles de familias colombianas accedan a un techo digno.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">*Agro</span>:* Un billón de pesos menos para el campo, un sector vital que no solo provee alimentos, sino que es el sustento de innumerables familias campesinas.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">*Salud</span>:* 1.8 billones de pesos menos, una cifra que en un país con tantas necesidades sanitarias, es inaceptable.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">*Deporte</span>:* Cuatro billones menos, lo que afecta el desarrollo de jóvenes talentos y la promoción de un estilo de vida saludable.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mientras se despojan estas áreas cruciales, se asignan 37 billones de pesos para «OPS y otros gastos públicos</span>«*. Esto genera una *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">paradoja fiscal*</span>&nbsp;que el Senador subraya con vehemencia: se recorta la inversión social para financiar gastos que parecen menos prioritarios o, peor aún, ineficientes.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El Senador Ramírez no se detiene en las cifras; también toca la falta de *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">diálogo y concertación*</span>. La crítica de que el gobierno no habla con alcaldes ni gobernadores revela un distanciamiento peligroso entre el poder central y las regiones. Si el presupuesto *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">se define sin la participación de quienes conocen las necesidades del territorio, es probable que las soluciones no se ajusten a la realidad*.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La frustración culmina en una predicción sombría: *»<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">la horrible noche cesará en nueve meses»*</span>. Esta frase, cargada de simbolismo, sugiere que la gestión actual ha defraudado a la ciudadanía. La promesa de *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">«hacer las cosas distintas»*</span>&nbsp;se ha quedado en palabras, mientras el *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">«derroche» y la «ineficiencia»*</span>&nbsp;persisten. La columna de opinión se convierte en un llamado a la *<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">rendición de cuentas</span>,* a un gobierno que se aleje de la demagogia y se acerque a las necesidades reales de su gente</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759189853_gf-703x570.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:50:53', '2025-09-29 23:50:53', '', '', ''),
(25, 'De Tlajomulco a Donbás: La exportación de la violencia colombiana', 'de-tlajomulco-a-donbas-la-exportacion-de-la-violencia-colombiana', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El reciente secuestro y posterior liberación de cinco ciudadanos colombianos en Tlajomulco de Zúñiga, Jalisco, es más que un simple incidente de extorsión. Este caso, que pudo haberse diluido como un episodio aislado de préstamos «gota a gota», en realidad nos confronta con un fenómeno mucho más profundo y preocupante: la creciente participación de colombianos, incluidos exintegrantes de la fuerza pública, como mano de obra criminal y combatientes en conflictos internacionales.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El hilo conductor entre un cobro violento en México y una trinchera en Ucrania es el mismo: la&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">exportación de un capital humano violento</span>. Ciudadanos colombianos, muchos de ellos con entrenamiento militar especializado en el conflicto interno del país, están siendo reclutados por redes criminales y mercenarias alrededor del mundo. La promesa de altos ingresos y la falta de oportunidades en su país natal se convierten en el motor que los lleva a cruzar fronteras.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En México, hemos visto cómo exmilitares colombianos no solo se vinculan a actividades de cobro de deudas, sino que también operan como instructores de tácticas de combate para carteles del narcotráfico. En Haití, la participación de un comando de exsoldados colombianos en el magnicidio del presidente Jovenel Moïse en 2021 demostró la capacidad de estos grupos para llevar a cabo operaciones de alto perfil. Y en Europa del Este, combatientes colombianos han sido reclutados por ambos bandos en la guerra entre Ucrania y Rusia, participando en misiones de asalto y manejo de armamento pesado.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Este fenómeno tiene consecuencias devastadoras. En primer lugar, afecta la imagen de Colombia en el escenario internacional, asociando al país con la violencia y el crimen organizado. Pero más allá de la reputación, esta «exportación de la violencia» desestabiliza regiones enteras, fortaleciendo a grupos criminales y prolongando conflictos armados. El caso de Tlajomulco, aunque resuelto, debe servir como una señal de alarma. Es un recordatorio de que la violencia no conoce fronteras y que los problemas internos de un país pueden tener un eco global.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Es crucial que las autoridades colombianas y la sociedad en general enfrenten este problema con seriedad. Se necesita una estrategia integral que aborde las causas de este fenómeno, como la falta de oportunidades laborales para los exmilitares, y que fortalezca la cooperación internacional para desmantelar estas redes de contratación criminal. De lo contrario, seguiremos viendo a colombianos, que alguna vez sirvieron a su país, convertirse en engranajes de la maquinaria del crimen organizado en cualquier rincón del planeta</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759190029_col.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:53:49', '2025-09-29 23:53:49', '', '', ''),
(26, 'Tormenta tropical Dexter agita el Atlántico y eleva la alerta por oleajes peligrosos', 'tormenta-tropical-dexter-agita-el-atlantico-y-eleva-la-alerta-por-oleajes-peligrosos', '<blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-image: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">La tormenta tropical Dexter se formó el domingo 3 de agosto sobre el noroeste del océano Atlántico, aproximadamente a 400 kilómetros de las Bermudas, según informó el Centro Nacional de Huracanes (NHC) de Estados Unidos. Aunque el fenómeno meteorológico no tocará tierra, su paso ya está generando preocupaciones por el fuerte oleaje y las peligrosas corrientes de resaca que afectarán a varias zonas costeras del este de EE.UU.</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Con vientos sostenidos de 75 kilómetros por hora, Dexter se desplaza en dirección noroeste a una velocidad de 22 km/h. Según expertos de AccuWeather, como el meteorólogo Alex DaSilva, el sistema influenciará la formación de mar picado a lo largo de la costa atlántica, generando condiciones riesgosas en playas muy concurridas en temporada de verano. También se prevén lluvias intensas y tormentas eléctricas alrededor de la Corriente del Golfo</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Aunque no hay alertas oficiales vigentes, se considera que el frente que originó esta tormenta aún podría dar paso a una nueva depresión tropical en el transcurso de la semana. Las regiones más expuestas a futuras afectaciones son las Carolinas, Georgia y Virginia, donde el riesgo de inundaciones repentinas aumentaría en caso de nuevos desarrollos ciclónicos.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La Administración Nacional Oceánica y Atmosférica (NOAA) anticipó una temporada de huracanes más activa de lo habitual en 2025, con hasta 19 tormentas con nombre. De estas, entre 6 y 10 podrían alcanzar la categoría de huracán, y hasta cinco serían considerados mayores, con vientos superiores a 179 km/h.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_4_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_4\" name=\"aswift_4\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=3338436699&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.16~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759190088&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Finternacional%2Ftormenta-tropical-dexter-agita-el-atlantico-y-eleva-la-alerta-por-oleajes-peligrosos%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759190088186&amp;bpp=16&amp;bdt=1468&amp;idt=16&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759189781%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759189781%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759189781%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280%2C726x280&amp;nras=2&amp;correlator=1185857806948&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=10&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=1846&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31094694%2C31094918%2C95367554%2C95372357%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1483740120935062&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Finternacional%2Fde-tlajomulco-a-donbas-la-exportacion-de-la-violencia-colombiana%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=480\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-query-id=\"CKyG5tCV_48DFW5vQQIdtAUxhw\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Las autoridades instan a la población costera a mantenerse informada y tomar medidas preventivas, como revisar planes de evacuación, reunir suministros y reforzar sus viviendas. Aunque Dexter no tocará tierra, sus efectos sí podrían sentirse fuertemente en las próximas horas</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759190150_DESTER-1140x570.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:55:50', '2025-09-29 23:55:50', '', '', ''),
(27, 'La Libertad de Expresión en la República Dominicana', 'la-libertad-de-expresion-en-la-republica-dominicana', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La libertad de expresión en República Dominicana, aunque protegida constitucionalmente, enfrenta desafíos en su ejercicio pleno. La Constitución y leyes como la 6132 reconocen este derecho, pero existen limitaciones y tensiones, especialmente en el ámbito de la prensa digital .</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El artículo 7 de nuestra constitución establece que La República Dominicana es un Estado Social y Democrático de Derecho, donde la dignidad humana debe y tiene que ser respetada .</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En su artículo 8 establece además como función esencial del Estado, la protección efectiva de esos derechos&nbsp;</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759190236_WhatsApp-Image-2025-08-04-at-17.24.24-1140x570.jpeg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-29 23:57:16', '2025-09-29 23:57:16', '', '', ''),
(28, 'Con Grandes Criticas Gobierno Reafirma Compromiso con la Zona Binacional con Venezuela', 'con-grandes-criticas-gobierno-reafirma-compromiso-con-la-zona-binacional-con-venezuela', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En la administración del presidente Gustavo Petro “reafirmamos nuestro compromiso con el desarrollo integral de las regiones fronterizas, garantizando la presencia del Estado, la seguridad y el bienestar de nuestra gente», manifestó este sábado el ministro del Interior, Armando Benedetti.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En diálogo con periodistas, el MinInterior explicó que “no se trata de ceder soberanía. Se trata de generar cooperación institucional para mejorar la vida de quienes habitan la frontera».</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_4_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_4\" name=\"aswift_4\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=4248172323&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.10~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759190411&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Finternacional%2Fcon-garndes-criticas-gobierno-reafirma-compromiso-con-la-zona-binacional-con-venezuela%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759190411656&amp;bpp=3&amp;bdt=1168&amp;idt=3&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190161%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190161%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190161%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280%2C726x280&amp;nras=2&amp;correlator=7901098723072&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=13&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=1471&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31093846%2C31094694%2C95366795%2C95372142%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=7705827573446451&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Finternacional%2F97520%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;cms=2&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=334\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-query-id=\"CPDm9OqW_48DFZsjBgAdpt05ZQ\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El área económica especial fue creada de manera oficial mediante un memorando de entendimiento firmado por representantes de ambas naciones, fue denominado Zona de Paz, Unión y Desarrollo y se establecerá en los estados de Táchira y Zulia –por el lado de Venezuela– y Norte de Santander, aunque el área definitiva está por definirse.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Las precisiones del titular de la cartera del Interior se produjeron horas después de un pronunciamiento del jefe de Estado, quien en su cuenta de X enfatizó que “una zona binacional no es entregar la soberanía de la Patria, es crear las condiciones sociales y económicas, que permitan que dos pueblos de sangre e historia comunes, puedan ser dueños de sus territorios, prosperen y vivan bien».</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La firma del Memorando de Entendimiento para crear la Zona de Paz, Unión y Desarrollo entre Colombia y Venezuela se presentó el viernes pasado en la ciudad de Caracas.</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759190466_PE-1140x570.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-30 00:01:06', '2025-09-30 00:01:06', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `blog_posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `image`, `author`, `status`, `deleted`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`) VALUES
(29, 'Javier ‘Chicharito’ Hernández enfrentó una sanción por comentarios considerados sexistas, instando a mujeres a roles tradicionales', 'javier-chicharito-hernandez-enfrento-una-sancion-por-comentarios-considerados-sexistas-instando-a-mujeres-a-roles-tradicionales', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Javier «Chicharito» Hernández, histórico goleador de la Selección Mexicana y actual delantero de las Chivas de Guadalajara, se encuentra en el centro de una controversia por sus recientes declaraciones que, según la Federación Mexicana de Fútbol (FMF), “promueven estereotipos sexistas”. Como consecuencia, el jugador fue sancionado con una multa económica y un apercibimiento, aunque el monto no fue revelado.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La polémica surgió a raíz de una serie de videos publicados por el futbolista en redes sociales, donde insta a las mujeres a «encarnar su energía femenina» asumiendo roles tradicionales como cuidar el hogar y apoyar a sus parejas hombres. En sus mensajes, también afirma que “las mujeres están fracasando” y acusa un intento de “erradicar la masculinidad”, lo que encendió alarmas tanto en el mundo del deporte como en el ámbito político y social.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_4_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_4\" name=\"aswift_4\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=4248172323&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.10~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759190611&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Finternacional%2Fjavier-chicharito-hernandez-enfrento-una-sancion-por-comentarios-considerados-sexistas-instando-a-mujeres-a-roles-tradicionales%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759190611733&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=1171&amp;idt=2&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190526%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190526%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190526%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280&amp;nras=2&amp;correlator=1669179836062&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=14&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=1601&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31094694%2C42532524%2C95372143%2C95372195%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=5971515492659116&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Finternacional%2Fcon-garndes-criticas-gobierno-reafirma-compromiso-con-la-zona-binacional-con-venezuela%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=251\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-query-id=\"CJnXocqX_48DFVFFHQkdQvsRAg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Las repercusiones no se hicieron esperar. La Comisión de Género y Diversidad de la FMF investigó el caso y aplicó sanciones, con la advertencia de que serán más severas en caso de reincidencia.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La presidenta de México, Claudia Sheinbaum, calificó las declaraciones como “una idea muy machista”. En su conferencia matutina del miércoles, Sheinbaum expresó que las mujeres “pueden ser lo que quieran ser” y defendió el principio constitucional de igualdad sustantiva: “No es por polemizar con Chicharito, pero sí es importante que todos los hombres reconozcan a las mujeres como personas con derechos plenos”.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La Secretaría de las Mujeres del Gobierno Federal respaldó el mensaje presidencial, calificando las palabras del jugador como “discursos sexistas, machistas y misóginos”. También llamó a eliminar estereotipos de género y defender el derecho de las mujeres a desarrollarse libremente</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759190778_gol-1140x570.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-30 00:06:18', '2025-09-30 00:06:18', '', '', ''),
(30, 'La Defensoría del Pueblo emitió una alerta por la grave situación de violencia en Cúcuta y municipios de Norte de Santander.', 'la-defensoria-del-pueblo-emitio-una-alerta-por-la-grave-situacion-de-violencia-en-cucuta-y-municipios-de-norte-de-santander', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Una grave situación de riesgo es la que enfrentan las comunidades de Cúcuta, Puerto Santander, Villa del Rosario y Los Patios, en el departamento de Norte de Santander, debido a la creciente presencia de grupos armados ilegales y organizaciones criminales. El Ejército de Liberación Nacional (ELN), el Ejército Gaitanista de Colombia (EGC) y diversas bandas de criminalidad organizada están generando un clima de violencia extrema en estas localidades, con impactos devastadores sobre la población civil.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Ante este panorama, la Defensoría del Pueblo emitió una alerta para llamar la atención sobre el control territorial que estos grupos ejercen mediante desplazamientos forzados, amenazas, homicidios selectivos, extorsiones y reclutamiento de menores de edad, lo que ha puesto en peligro la vida de miles de personas. «Esta situación afecta especialmente a personas defensoras de derechos humanos, lideresas y líderes sociales, comerciantes, población migrante, jóvenes, mujeres y comunidades vulnerables que se encuentran en un alto riesgo de victimización», afirmó Iris Marín Ortiz, señaló la defensora del Pueblo.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_4_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_4\" name=\"aswift_4\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=4248172323&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.10~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759190921&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fla-defensoria-del-pueblo-emitio-una-alerta-por-la-grave-situacion-de-violencia-en-cucuta-y-municipios-de-norte-de-santander%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759190920945&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=1275&amp;idt=2&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190526%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190526%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190526%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280&amp;nras=2&amp;correlator=2270645469781&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=15&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=1720&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31094858%2C31094918%2C42531705%2C95370627%2C95372195%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=5039880077961727&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Finternacional%2Fjavier-chicharito-hernandez-enfrento-una-sancion-por-comentarios-considerados-sexistas-instando-a-mujeres-a-roles-tradicionales%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=337\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-query-id=\"CNn13N2Y_48DFVkwaAgdUe4Rkw\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En la región, el ELN ha consolidado su presencia en las zonas rurales de Cúcuta y Puerto Santander, mientras que el EGC ha extendido sus acciones criminales hacia áreas urbanas, lo que ha provocado una creciente inseguridad. Además, bandas criminales como el ‘Tren de Aragua’, ‘AK-47’ y ‘Los del Norte’ han incrementado su influencia en el departamento, controlando el microtráfico, la trata de personas y el tráfico de migrantes, y utilizando los pasos fronterizos como rutas estratégicas para actividades ilícitas.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La alerta también resalta la grave situación socioeconómica en las zonas afectadas, donde altos niveles de pobreza, la falta de acceso a servicios básicos y la escasa oferta laboral contribuyen a la vulnerabilidad de la población. “En este contexto, niños, niñas y adolescentes, especialmente de la comunidad indígena Yukpa, están siendo explotados en actividades ilegales, lo que agrava la crisis humanitaria en la región”.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Ante esta alarmante situación, la Defensora del Pueblo hizo un llamado urgente a los gobiernos nacional, departamental y local para que coordinen acciones concretas para proteger los derechos humanos en la región. «Es fundamental fortalecer la presencia institucional en las áreas más afectadas por el accionar de los grupos armados no estatales y bandas criminales, garantizar la atención humanitaria a las comunidades vulnerables y promover estrategias de prevención que permitan mitigar los riesgos a los que se enfrentan miles de personas en Norte de Santander», destacó Iris Marín Ortiz.</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759191026_GRUPOS.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-30 00:10:26', '2025-09-30 00:10:26', '', '', ''),
(31, 'Del 5,3 % Incremento de la UPC para 2025 representa un ‘ascenso real’ respecto a 2024”, Petro', 'del-5-3-incremento-de-la-upc-para-2025-representa-un-ascenso-real-respecto-a-2024-petro', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Para la vigencia 2025, según lo anunció el Ministerio de Salud y Protección Social, el valor de la Unidad de Pago por Capitación (UPC) tendrá un incremento del 5,3 %, adoptado con base en la inflación causada a noviembre de 2024 y la actualización en servicios y tecnologías en salud.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">“Esta decisión responde a la necesidad de proteger los recursos del Sistema de Seguridad Social en Salud ante la imposibilidad de efectuar un cálculo, debido a la baja calidad, poca confiabilidad y las inconsistencias detectadas en la información reportada por las EPS”, explicó esta cartera a través de un boletín de prensa, al anunciar el incremento de la UPC para 2025.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_4_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_4\" name=\"aswift_4\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=4248172323&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.10~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759191151&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fdel-53-incremento-de-la-upc-para-2025-representa-un-ascenso-real-respecto-a-2024-petro%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759191151620&amp;bpp=6&amp;bdt=988&amp;idt=6&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190883%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190883%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190883%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280&amp;nras=2&amp;correlator=7938953591451&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=1594&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95366176%2C95372730%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=6114643191149800&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fla-defensoria-del-pueblo-emitio-una-alerta-por-la-grave-situacion-de-violencia-en-cucuta-y-municipios-de-norte-de-santander%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=333\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-query-id=\"CM6Q3suZ_48DFVlJHQkdgQwUHw\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Al respecto, en un mensaje publicado en su cuenta de X, el presidente Gustavo Petro manifestó que el “incremento de la UPC (del 5,3 % para 2025), representa un ascenso real respecto al pasado”.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El mandatario explicó que “la tasa de inflación de 5,4 % como medida de la UPC ya se produjo. Es inflación causada en el 2024 y no la esperada en el 2025”.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Agregó que “si la inflación esperada es 3 % (para 2025), el incremento de la UPC para salud tiene 2,4 % de incremento real sobre la inflación y ya puede subsumir el costo laboral que se incrementa en el salario mínimo del 9,4 %”.</p><h3 style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.563em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Razones del incremento de la UPC para 2025</span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Por su parte, el viceministro de Protección Social, Luis Alberto Martínez, emitió una declaración en la cual reiteró que la información reportada por las EPS, con base en la cual se calcula el incremento de la UPC, presentó en esta ocasión “serias inconsistencias</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Indicó que, por ejemplo, en dicha información reportada por las EPS “hay un crecimiento abrupto, inusitado, en los valores y en las frecuencias de uso, lo que no guarda consistencia ni con los datos históricos ni con el perfil epidemiológico del país”.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Asimismo, expuso que las “EPS que certificaron el gasto no tienen todavía cerrado financieramente el año 2023. No está firmado por el revisor fiscal ni por el representante legal”.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_5_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_5\" name=\"aswift_5\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=2181186569&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.27~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759191152&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fdel-53-incremento-de-la-upc-para-2025-representa-un-ascenso-real-respecto-a-2024-petro%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759191151635&amp;bpp=7&amp;bdt=1003&amp;idt=7&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190883%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190883%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190883%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280%2C750x280&amp;nras=3&amp;correlator=7938953591451&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=2395&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95366176%2C95372730%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=6114643191149800&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fla-defensoria-del-pueblo-emitio-una-alerta-por-la-grave-situacion-de-violencia-en-cucuta-y-municipios-de-norte-de-santander%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=6&amp;uci=a!6&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=1024\" data-google-container-id=\"a!6\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-google-query-id=\"CM6uicyZ_48DFdVcHQkdGGoE9w\" data-load-complete=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El viceministro informó que, adicionalmente, “se pagaron precios a medicamentos que tienen control de precios y se pagaron por encima del precio que está establecido”, todo lo cual “genera mucha incertidumbre sobre esta información”.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Esta situación –sostuvo– llevó a que la Comisión Asesora de Beneficios, Costos y Tarifas del Aseguramiento “recomendara al Ministerio de Salud que se estableciera una UPC cercana al Índice de Precios al Consumidor (IPC), es decir, cercana al 5,2 %”.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_6_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_6\" name=\"aswift_6\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=250&amp;adk=740097205&amp;adf=2368990370&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.31~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759191182&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x250&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fdel-53-incremento-de-la-upc-para-2025-representa-un-ascenso-real-respecto-a-2024-petro%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759191151666&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=1035&amp;idt=2&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190883%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190883%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759190883%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280%2C750x280%2C750x280%2C726x280&amp;nras=4&amp;correlator=7938953591451&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=2591&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=247&amp;eid=95366176%2C95372730%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=6114643191149800&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=3&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fla-defensoria-del-pueblo-emitio-una-alerta-por-la-grave-situacion-de-violencia-en-cucuta-y-municipios-de-norte-de-santander%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=6&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=30395\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-google-query-id=\"COaPj9qZ_48DFZpHHQkd4TwqHA\" data-load-complete=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En consecuencia, la decisión fue incrementar en 5,3 % la UPC para 2025, manifestó el viceministro.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El Ministerio de Salud define la Unidad de Pago por Capitación (UPC) como el valor anual que se reconoce por cada uno de los afiliados al Sistema General de Seguridad Social en Salud para cubrir las prestaciones del Plan Obligatorio de Salud (POS), en los regímenes contributivo y subsidiado.</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759191272_UPC.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-30 00:14:32', '2025-09-30 00:14:32', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `blog_posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `image`, `author`, `status`, `deleted`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`) VALUES
(32, 'Iván NAME Vásquez enfrenta pérdida de investidura', 'ivan-name-vasquez-enfrenta-perdida-de-investidura', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \"Droid Serif\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">La sala de Instrucción Penal de la Corte Suprema de Justicia</span><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: \"Droid Serif\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> </em><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \"Droid Serif\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">decretó pruebas dentro de la demanda de pérdida de investidura contra el senador de la Alianza Verde </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: \"Droid Serif\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Iván Leonidas Name Vásquez,</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \"Droid Serif\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"> por estar inmerso en tráfico de influencias en los procesos de contratación de la Unidad Nacional para la Gestión del Riesgo de Desastres (UNGRD). El despacho del magistrado Jorge Edison Portocarrero ordenó la revisión de las entrevistas e interrogatorios rendidos ante la Corte Suprema de Justicia como ante la fiscalía general por el exdirector de la UNGRD, Olmedo López Martínez, y en la que estaría confirmado la participación del congresista Name en este entramado de corrupción</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: \"Droid Serif\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Igualmente, se pidió recolectar versiones públicas dadas por el exsubdirector de la UNGRD Sneyder Pinilla, en las que ha mencionado al congresista de la Alianza Verde y su participación en la entrega de millonarios sobornos para nueve parlamentarios. <a href=\"https://www.semana.com/nacion/articulo/corrupcion-en-la-ungrd-inadmiten-demanda-que-busca-la-muerte-politica-para-el-senador-ivan-name/202453/?ref=elfrente.com.co\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(252, 124, 12);\">En la demanda de pérdida de investidura firmada por Juan Carlos Calderón España, presidente de la Veeduría Ciudadana Nacional Recursos Sagrados, se advierte que el congresista de la Alianza Verde utilizó su cargo para influenciar en la celebración de millonarios contratos de obra de la UNGRD.</a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: \"Droid Serif\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Los hechos se presentaron tras la firma del polémico contrato para la compra de 40 carrotanques que tenían como fin llevar agua potable al departamento de La Guajira. “El señor Iván Leónidas Name Vásquez faltó a sus deberes constitucionales y legales, pues las evidencias conducen a que este mismo obtuvo un proyecto personal que fue el dinero recibido, obtenido gracias a su investidura de <a href=\"https://www.semana.com/nacion/articulo/urgente-sneyder-pinilla-propone-pagar-cinco-anos-de-prision-y-devolver-292-millones-de-pesos/202457/?ref=elfrente.com.co\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(252, 124, 12);\">congresista y presidente del Senado </a>y, aún peor, representando la máxima institución de la Rama Legislativa”, señala uno de los apartes de la demanda firmada por el veedor ciudadano</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759191622_ivan.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-30 00:20:22', '2025-09-30 00:24:14', '', '', ''),
(33, 'Proyecto de Ley «Salva un Árbol»', 'proyecto-de-ley-salva-un-arbol', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">El proyecto de ley «Salva un Árbol»,</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;presentado por el de Toledo, Norte de Santander , miembro del Partido En Marcha, el&nbsp; senador Jairo Alberto Castellanos Serrano,</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;busca incentivar el reciclaje de madera en Colombia para</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">reducir la tala indiscriminada de árboles y promover la reforestación. Este proyecto establece medidas obligatorias para que los municipios destinen terrenos para centros de acopio de madera reciclable y fomenta el uso de biomasa en la industria maderera.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Puntos Clave del Proyecto de Ley:</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">1. Objetivo Principal: Incentivar el reciclaje de madera para reducir la tala de árboles, evitar que desechos de madera terminen en rellenos sanitarios, ríos</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">o calles, y promover la fabricación de tableros aglomerados a partir de biomasa.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">2. Obligaciones Municipales: Todos los municipios deben disponer de al menos dos hectáreas para acopiar madera reciclable y un mínimo de media hectárea para viveros de árboles. Además, deberán contar con vehículos recolectores y maquinaria para procesar la madera reciclada.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">3. Beneficios Ambientales: Por cada 400 kg de madera reciclada se evitará la tala de un árbol de 10 años de edad y se sembrarán cinco árboles adicionales</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">por cada familia al año, contribuyendo significativamente a la conservación del medio ambiente.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">4. Impacto en el Empleo: Se estima la creación de más de 70,000 empleos directos en todo el país, especialmente para madres cabeza de hogar, discapacitados y reinsertados de grupos al margen de la ley, quienes serán responsables de tareas como la recolección, reciclaje, y reforestación.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">5. Educación y Cultura Ambiental: Las instituciones educativas deberán implementar espacios para recolectar y reciclar partículas de biomasa</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">generadas por lápices y otros implementos, fomentando una cultura de reciclaje desde edades tempranas.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">6. Incentivos Tributarios: Las empresas que manejen correctamente la separación y reciclaje de madera obtendrán beneficios tributarios, fomentando su participación en la iniciativa</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></p>', 'public/images/blog/1759191836_WhatsApp-Image-2024-09-22-at-19.44.00-1140x570.jpeg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-30 00:23:56', '2025-09-30 00:23:56', '', '', ''),
(34, 'EL Senador Miguel Uribe denuncia que contratación en la Agencia Nacional de Tierras creció más del 300% en un año', 'el-senador-miguel-uribe-denuncia-que-contratacion-en-la-agencia-nacional-de-tierras-crecio-mas-del-300-en-un-ano', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Durante la plenaria del Senado, el congresista del Centro Democrático&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Miguel Uribe</span>&nbsp;hizo pública una denuncia que compromete al Gobierno Nacional y sus planes de austeridad, en momentos en que se habla de recortes presupuestales y de problemas financieros y de liquidez.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">De acuerdo con el senador del partido de oposición, en 2023 el gobierno&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Petro suscribió 1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">16.229 contratos, la cifra más alta desde 2018</span>, con un gasto de $8,36 billones y un incremento del 54% con relación a los dos primeros años de la administración de Iván Duque.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_4_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_4\" name=\"aswift_4\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=4248172323&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.10~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759191985&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fel-senador-miguel-uribe-denuncia-que-contratacion-en-la-agencia-nacional-de-tierras-crecio-mas-del-300-en-un-ano%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759191985277&amp;bpp=3&amp;bdt=1152&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759191674%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759191674%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759191674%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280&amp;nras=2&amp;correlator=7272416333581&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=21&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=1566&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31094857%2C95372357%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1103286085163817&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fproyecto-de-ley-salva-un-arbol%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=151\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-google-query-id=\"CKzOk9mc_48DFTMaaAgd34oqDg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Uribe, sin embargo, llamó la atención de manera particular sobre la situación de la&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Agencia Nacional de Tierras (ANT),</span>&nbsp;en donde según las indagaciones que adelantó junto con su equipo de trabajo, la contratación&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">aumentó en un 309%</span>&nbsp;entre 2022 y 2023, al pasar de 1.161 a 4.753 contratos, y un presupuesto de $67.000 millones a&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">$236.000 millones</span>&nbsp;en apenas un año.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La tendencia para 2024 se mantiene, asegura el congresista, puesto que en el primer semestre esa entidad ya ha celebrado 4.853 contratos.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_5_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_5\" name=\"aswift_5\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=615410430&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.14~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759191985&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fel-senador-miguel-uribe-denuncia-que-contratacion-en-la-agencia-nacional-de-tierras-crecio-mas-del-300-en-un-ano%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759191985277&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=1151&amp;idt=2&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759191674%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759191674%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759191674%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280%2C750x280&amp;nras=3&amp;correlator=7272416333581&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=21&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=2042&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31094857%2C95372357%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1103286085163817&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fproyecto-de-ley-salva-un-arbol%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=6&amp;uci=a!6&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=154\" data-google-container-id=\"a!6\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-query-id=\"CO-qlNmc_48DFf0kaAgdg7QMFA\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El dirigente cuestionó que el “derroche” que se viene observando en esta entidad contrasta con la baja ejecución de las metas trazadas en el Plan de Desarrollo en materia de tierras, puesto que en&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">estos momentos ese avance es del cero por ciento lo que</span>, en su criterio, refleja una falta de gestión y cumplimiento de las promesas gubernamentales.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El sector de la agricultura tiene una de las ejecuciones presupuestales más bajas (13,4%), solo por encima del sector deporte y de Presidencia. Las principales entidades adscritas y vinculadas al sector tienen ejecuciones de inversión por debajo del 25%.&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">La de la ANT es penosa, de solo 5,6%”,</span>&nbsp;aseguró Uribe.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El senador manifestó ante la plenaria que lo grave del asunto es que durante el cotejo de la información lograron detectar que los beneficiarios de esos contratos son, principalmente,&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">“amigos del Gobierno”</span>&nbsp;y no técnicos, como ameritaría esta Agencia.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_6_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_6\" name=\"aswift_6\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=2368990370&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.23~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759191985&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fel-senador-miguel-uribe-denuncia-que-contratacion-en-la-agencia-nacional-de-tierras-crecio-mas-del-300-en-un-ano%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759191985285&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=1160&amp;idt=2&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759191674%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759191674%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759191674%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C726x280%2C345x280%2C750x280%2C750x280&amp;nras=4&amp;correlator=7272416333581&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=21&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=2347&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31094857%2C95372357%2C95368094&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1103286085163817&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Fpolitica%2Fproyecto-de-ley-salva-un-arbol%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=5&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=542\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-query-id=\"CO-KrNmc_48DFUEuaAgdxJkRSA\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">“Es alarmante la contratación masiva de operadores políticos afines al&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pacto Histórico y la Alianza Verde&nbsp;</span>dentro de la ANT, con más de 74 personas que participaron en elecciones territoriales en 2019 y 55 más de las elecciones de 2023, hoy vinculadas contractualmente con la entidad”, señaló el dirigente del Centro Democrático.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Miguel Uribe mencionó, por ejemplo, el caso del exsenador&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Antonio Sanguino,</span>&nbsp;de quien aseguró que tiene varios contratos, algunos de ellos en la Agencia de Tierras, “además de que son vergonzosos los informes que presenta”.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Denunció que el propio director de la ANT,&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Juan Felipe Harman</span>, exalcalde de Villavicencio, contrató a un exconcejal de ese municipio como médico, con un salario de $11 millones y “¡óigase bien!, en 30 días solo atendió cinco pacientes”. &nbsp;Agregó que, “<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Lo más grave es que también contrató al hermano por $15 millones</span>”.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El congresista anunció que tras los hallazgos detectados, radicarán una queja ante la Procuraduría General de la Nación y la Contraloría General de la República, para que se investigue lo sucedido con la contratación en la ANT y de ser el caso sancione a los responsables del derroche de recursos públicos.</p>', 'public/images/blog/1759192103_uribe.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-30 00:28:23', '2025-09-30 00:28:23', '', '', ''),
(35, 'Yina Calderón revela su excéntrico regalo de cumpleaños: un carro eléctrico Mini-San temático de Dragon Ball Z, que es automático y práctico', 'yina-calderon-revela-su-excentrico-regalo-de-cumpleanos-un-carro-electrico-mini-san-tematico-de-dragon-ball-z-que-es-automatico-y-practico', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La empresaria y DJ Yina Calderón volvió a ser tendencia en redes sociales tras revelar el excéntrico regalo de cumpleaños que se hizo a sí misma: un carro eléctrico completamente personalizado con temática de&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Dragon Ball Z</em>. El vehículo, un Mini-San de la marca TG, fue mostrado en su cuenta de Instagram, donde tiene más de 800 mil seguidores. “Están a punto de conocer mi Saya Móvil”, dijo Calderón antes de quitarle la tela roja que lo cubría.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">El automóvil no solo llama la atención por su diseño inspirado en el anime japonés, sino también por ser eléctrico, lo que Calderón destacó como una ventaja: “No tiene pico y placa, no gasta en gasolina y hay parqueaderos donde no se paga”. En los videos que compartió, enseñó el interior del carro y resaltó su practicidad: “Es automático, se maneja fácil, tiene radio, luces y cabe en cualquier lado”.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Las reacciones no se hicieron esperar. Mientras algunos celebraron el estilo único de Yina, otros no fueron tan entusiastas. Comentarios como “qué boleta, apenas para ella”, “es tan ella que me duelen los ojos”, o “parece un juguete”, contrastaron con otros que lo calificaron de “tierno” y “muy lindo</p><div class=\"adsb30\" style=\"margin: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-ad-slot=\"3244135814\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; background: transparent !important; height: auto !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_1_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 726px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: visible; height: auto !important;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: initial !important; width: 726px !important; display: flex !important; flex-wrap: wrap !important; place-content: center !important; align-items: center !important; gap: 10px !important; height: auto !important; max-height: 280px !important;\"></div></div></ins></div>', 'public/images/blog/1759192292_gina-981x570.jpg', 'Ana Maria Daza', 'published', 0, '2025-09-30 00:31:32', '2025-09-30 00:31:32', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `blog_posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `image`, `author`, `status`, `deleted`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`) VALUES
(36, 'Katuche la Tiene clara y resalta que “La katecumbia es como una revolución pacífica, una revolución bailada, una revolución que Une a grandes y a chicos', 'katuche-la-tiene-clara-y-resalta-que-la-katecumbia-es-como-una-revolucion-pacifica-una-revolucion-bailada-una-revolucion-que-une-a-grandes-y-a-chicos', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La cumbia, un género musical y baile tradicional colombiano, ha tenido una evolución significativa a lo largo de su historia, fusionando influencias africanas, latinoamericanas y europeas.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Se caracteriza por su ritmo alegre y sensual, reflejo de la historia y el mestizaje cultural de América Latina.&nbsp;La cumbia moderna incorpora una variedad de instrumentos, incluyendo aquellos típicos del Caribe, y suele tener una voz que guía el baile.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_4_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px; width: 750px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_4\" name=\"aswift_4\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"750\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-4829843907633909&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=144910138&amp;adf=4248172323&amp;pi=t.aa~a.369024205~i.10~rp.4&amp;w=750&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1759192342&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=7807067007&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=750x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Ffarandula%2Fkatuche258%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=188&amp;rw=750&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTQwLjAuNzMzOS4yMDgiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxNDAuMC43MzM5LjIwOCJdLFsiTm90PUE_QnJhbmQiLCIyNC4wLjAuMCJdLFsiR29vZ2xlIENocm9tZSIsIjE0MC4wLjczMzkuMjA4Il1dLDBd&amp;abgtt=9&amp;dt=1759192341954&amp;bpp=3&amp;bdt=1360&amp;idt=3&amp;shv=r20250925&amp;mjsv=m202509230101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D10ab754ce0503ae9%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759192165%3AS%3DALNI_MYgPhx2hjraAFgh0Ou95EV6pTtpng&amp;gpic=UID%3D000012961a477675%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759192165%3AS%3DALNI_MZgPFb9MTQ7YADSPSK0N1EnmpCo-A&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc9b3f443f534cd8c%3AT%3D1759184978%3ART%3D1759192165%3AS%3DAA-AfjbWzN1Fy8SXyjSZhB22xUiJ&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C345x280%2C726x280&amp;nras=2&amp;correlator=1089560277564&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=-300&amp;u_his=24&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=720&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=106&amp;ady=1593&amp;biw=1351&amp;bih=633&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31094694%2C95372138%2C95372358%2C95344788%2C95368094%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=7542515238542498&amp;tmod=649807193&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caucaextremo.com%2Ffarandula%2Fyina-calderon-revela-su-excentrico-regalo-de-cumpleanos-un-carro-electrico-mini-san-tematico-de-dragon-ball-z-que-es-automatico-y-practico%2F&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C720%2C1366%2C633&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLDNd&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuOC4y~CAEQBRoGMy4yNy43&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=280\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" data-load-complete=\"true\" data-google-query-id=\"CK_0p4Oe_48DFVlMQQIdW3IRKw\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: none; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 750px; height: 0px; min-height: auto; max-height: none; min-width: auto;\"></iframe></div></ins></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">La cumbia es más que un simple baile;&nbsp;es un símbolo de identidad cultural y cohesión social.&nbsp;En el Cauca, se considera un factor de cohesión social y un medio para expresar emociones y sentimientos, conectando a las personas a través de la música y el baile lo cual nuestro artista&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">“katuche“ &nbsp;&nbsp;y su #katucumbia&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;hace disfrutar con sus ritmos a todos por igual .</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">En el año hay muchas fiestas donde la cumbia, el bugalú y el soul, sonidos lejanos al reguetón y al rap, ponen a bailar a caucanos &nbsp;&nbsp;y extranjeros sin olvidar esos intérpretes de música de despecho que saca del corazón el amor o desamores.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A las pocas fiestas a las cuales he asistido me he encontrado en un punto de la noche en el cual la cumbia suena, las personas bailan y corean, independientemente si es época decembrina o no.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Nacer y crecer en Colombia sin haber escuchado a Pastor López, Rodolfo Aicardi, Los Hispanos o Los Graduados es algo imposible de creer.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Quien puede negar que “Escucho cumbia desde los seis años e incluso antes de conocer el rock escuchaba las cumbias. A medida que fui madurando me empezaron a gustar más o no.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Cada género musical ha tenido su punto auge, y dependiendo de los contextos sociales y culturales se populariza un género específico. Pasó, por ejemplo, con el rock o el reggae, que son géneros que constantemente tienen sube y bajas en la industria musical, pero con la cumbia ocurre algo particular.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">“He pensado que la cumbia va a superar el reguetón y, de hecho, a pesar de que no me guste ese género, algo que destaco es que al extranjero no le interesaba el español.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 750px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-4829843907633909\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 0px; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><div id=\"aswift_5_host\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; font: inherit; vert